timeline.bodyText:
I would suggest to swap the order of parameters here and rename the method.
The current order is unintuitive in my opinion or at least in a grammatical sense. If the method was called "canBePushedBy" then the current order would make more sense. So I am in favour of swapping these here.
Also if you want this to be overridden, then it should be at least protected.




        Suggested change











                private boolean canMoveEntity(@Nonnull LivingEntity entity, @Nonnull Player player) {



